			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is not possible to have more than one veiwport to my knowlede, but you can have all of your windows set up outside of it. I run my ui that way.
<br />
When adjusting the viewport there are four numbers to enter: x y xx yy. These are to adjust the position of the veiwport (x,y) and the size of the vieport (xx, yy). It will take some playing around to get the correct placement you want, but it makes it worth it imo to see everything without obstruction.<br />_________________<br />Daarr
<br />
Shards of Time
<br />
Saryrn Server</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
