			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In the game.
<br />

<br />
I have two hotkeys set up on bank 2. The first says:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">/viewport 190 10 1100 800</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
(This is my default viewport size, playing in 1600x1200 resolution)
<br />

<br />
the second says:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">/viewport reset</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
(This sets the viewport to full screen)
<br />

<br />
That way if I want to take a screenshot, I can turn off all the windows and increase my viewport to the full screen, then switch back with two keystrokes.<br />_________________<br /><br><div align=center><img src="http://www.shootingiron.com/tipop/notherkrag.jpg" width="500" height="200" border="0" usemap="#nothermap"><map name="nothermap"><area alt="Fury of Faith" coords="31,157,152,187" href="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/fury"><area alt="Tipop's Homepage" coords="186,157,321,187"  href="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/"><area alt="Kraggan's Magelo Profile" coords="342,157,465,186" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=120506"></map></div></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
