				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's NOT a mask, /viewport does scale the 3-d image. The 2-d interface overlays are unaffected, if that's what you were trying to move. If what you really want is a black area around the edges of everything, I suggest adjusting your monitor instead.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
